	  trunk/ardesia/src/scripts/recordmydesktop_screencast.sh,
	  trunk/ardesia/src/text_widget.c, 
          trunk/ardesia/src/utils.c:
          - In order to have a live streaming supports 
            1) Install icecast server and configure it 
            2) Change the file recordmydesktop_screencast.sh to enable 
               the live screencast and adjust it to point to the right server
            3) Install oggfwd tool 
            4) Run ardesia 
            5) Start the recorder (even the livestream willstart) 
            6) Enjoy Ardesia make a screencast with recordmydesktop
	       and it is sent to icecast with oggfwd
            All is done with theora/ogg patents free formats and with free software
            Now you can make a presentation and stream on the Net


